    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《疯狂动物城》是一款超高自由度的自走棋游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从200+动物英雄中组建您的动物战队，战胜其他对手。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏最多支持64人同房竞技。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >所有核心内容免费：所有会影响游戏胜利的事物都可以通过免费代币购买，不充钱一样能</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >完美体验游戏！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139480/extras/725ee7e66ae7b81a45c333845af162a4.avif?t=1728468844\" width=800 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 竞技模式</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >和其他7人进行激烈的同步游戏，燃烧自己的聪明才智，在每轮有限的时间里搭建出最合适的阵容。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >淘汰其他所有的玩家，拿下冠军！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 练习模式</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不限时间的异步多人模式。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在一轮一轮的战斗中不断优化自己的阵容，又或者尝试全新的阵容。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在失去所有心之前，拿下10场比赛的胜利！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 自定义模式</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一切规则由你决定，人数、血量、时间、甚至阵容，这个房间你说了算！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >和最多其他63名玩家享受你们的定制对局吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139480/extras/b14180c4d44ec93a584f26e25114398f.avif?t=1728468844\" width=800 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 森林（默认卡组）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >初始即可使用的卡组，简单但不平庸。所有玩家都可使用，自定义公平对局的不二选择！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139480/extras/112b192bb9db162eb3c99ac727e6bec9.poster.avif?t=1728468844\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139480/extras/112b192bb9db162eb3c99ac727e6bec9.webm?t=1728468844\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139480/extras/112b192bb9db162eb3c99ac727e6bec9.mp4?t=1728468844\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 花仙子</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不断的累计鲜花，召唤极其强力的花仙子为你而战！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139480/extras/1ab4ff4896eb5c89e145eada76ac0ce0.poster.avif?t=1728468844\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139480/extras/1ab4ff4896eb5c89e145eada76ac0ce0.webm?t=1728468844\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139480/extras/1ab4ff4896eb5c89e145eada76ac0ce0.mp4?t=1728468844\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 猫仙人</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >打乱敌人原有的阵型，让对方手足无措吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139480/extras/db23ab310542e70201aa13c973fc7fbb.poster.avif?t=1728468844\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139480/extras/db23ab310542e70201aa13c973fc7fbb.webm?t=1728468844\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139480/extras/db23ab310542e70201aa13c973fc7fbb.mp4?t=1728468844\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 哥布林</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在不断获得特性中逐渐变成最强队伍！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139480/extras/21edbaa542ee18e4bcd0d69b87bc50c4.poster.avif?t=1728468844\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139480/extras/21edbaa542ee18e4bcd0d69b87bc50c4.webm?t=1728468844\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139480/extras/21edbaa542ee18e4bcd0d69b87bc50c4.mp4?t=1728468844\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 自定义</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自由的选择你喜欢的卡牌，组成一套最适合自己玩法的独特卡组！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >开动你的脑筋，开发出全新的卡牌构筑，让你的对手大开眼界吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139480/extras/7b55425e2253f8beb758bea8bf46f486.poster.avif?t=1728468844\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139480/extras/7b55425e2253f8beb758bea8bf46f486.webm?t=1728468844\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139480/extras/7b55425e2253f8beb758bea8bf46f486.mp4?t=1728468844\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们也为玩家提供了预设卡组的运营思路和定阵卡牌，并会在对局内做星标推荐。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >所以轻松愉快的进行游玩吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139480/extras/268208b84c2341f3313c3e0e75a17215.avif?t=1728468844\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >目前游戏处于EA阶段，后续我们还会为动物园增添更多可爱的动物、装扮、道具等。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >极速更新，敬请期待！</p>",
